title: On the Moon
alt: "I believe that this nation should commit itself to achieving the goal, before this decade is out, of landing a man on Venus and returning him safely to--" [an aide frantically whispers in the president's ear for a moment] "... of landing a man on Venus."
transcript:
[Cueball and Megan are walking together.]
Cueball: If we could land a man on the Moon, why can't we-
Megan: -land a man on the Moon?
Cueball: ...ok, fair. But we're working on it, OK?
